# Stage 0 test: 3D beam with a mid-span rectangular notch.
# The generator suppresses point placement strictly inside the notch box;
# the converter-side companion (3DNotchDeleteQhull) drops elements whose
# midpoint falls inside the same box via `#@notch ... delete`.
#@output nodes.dat
#@domain 3
#@diam 0.008
#@maxiter 100000
#@perflag 3 0 0 0
#@ranint -1
#@ranflag 1
# bounding-box corners widen the localiser
#@vertex 1 coords 3 -0.01 -0.01 -0.01 refine 1. radius 0.
#@vertex 2 coords 3  0.11  0.06  0.06 refine 1. radius 0.
#@controlvertex 1 coords 3 0.0  0.025 0.025
#@controlvertex 2 coords 3 0.10 0.025 0.025
#@prism 1 box 6 0. 0. 0. 0.10 0.05 0.05 refine 1.
#@notch 1 box 6 0.045 0.0 0.0 0.055 0.025 0.05
